OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTop economist calls for    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'lenient' migration rules  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, It "absolutely makes sense" to be      
OL,6, lenient with migration rules when firms
OL,7, face staff shortages, the former chief 
OL,8, economist of the Bank of England says. 
OL,10,FAndy Haldane told the BBC the UK should
OL,11,Fbe "liberal in our visa policies" to   
OL,12,Ffill skills gaps, and that in turn     
OL,13,Fwould help to grow the economy.        
OL,15,FIt comes after the prime minister said 
OL,16,Flegal migration was too high.          
OL,18,FThe Home Office said its system allowed
OL,19,Fin the skills needed while encouraging 
OL,20,Finvestment in the domestic workforce.  
